rComments: Really difficult to pay attention to this class. He seems like a very nice person, but my disinterest mixed with his European accent equaled a very boring lecture. Not a lot of work and effort for this class, plus my textbook had all the answers in the back (and he got all the homework from the book, that was nice) do the work and you can get an A.
This class was super easy.  We were allowed a cheat sheet for each midterm and two for the final.  Also, he really doesn't expect that much from you.  Easy A, though.
